Jill Talley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jill_Talley 0 Jill Talley (born December 19, 1962) is an American actress and comedian. She is known for her work as a cast member of Mr. Show, voicing Karen on SpongeBob SquarePants, Sarah Dubois and various other characters on Adult Swim's The Boondocks, Nina, Gretchen and Ms. Mucus on Camp Lazlo, and Rita Loud on The Loud House. She often collaborates with her husband and fellow actor Tom Kenny. Jill_Talley ( born December_19_,_1962 ) is an_American_actress_and_comedian .
